      "title": "Dashboard Overview",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "## Code Generation Overview\nThis dashboard focuses on how Copilot contributes to code generation across the enterprise. It highlights lines of code added and deleted, generation versus acceptance activity, feature and IDE breakdowns, and pull request signals so teams can judge the breadth and quality of AI-assisted coding.\n\n**Tip:** set the time range to at least **Last 60 days** if you want February and March on the same view. February will only appear if those daily records were backfilled into VictoriaMetrics.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_VICTORIAMETRICS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "decimals": 0,
